ItemDesc: The dust that falls from the Amber Lord's body when they swing the divine hammer. Used to level up Traces slightly for <color=#f29e38ff>Preservation</color> characters.
ItemBGDesc: The guards at Pier Point have never left their posts on Qlipoth's orbit, simply waiting for a miracle that only occurs once in decades or even centuries — How stardust splutters up like countless raindrops the moment the giant hammer falls.\n\n"The stardust are simply insignificant dust to the Amber Lord, but to us, every speck of it contains the essence of Preservation."
